      <h2 parentName="article" {...{
        "id": "graduate-to-form-and-add-pending-ui"
      }}>{`Graduate to `}<inlineCode parentName="h2">{`<Form>`}</inlineCode>{` and add pending UI`}</h2>
      <p parentName="article">{`Let's use progressive enhancement to make this UX a bit more fancy. By changing it from `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`<form>`}</inlineCode>{` to `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`<Form>`}</inlineCode>{`, Remix will emulate the browser behavior with `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`fetch`}</inlineCode>{` and then give you access to the pending form information to build pending UI.`}</p>
